description: The index follows a rules-based methodology that tracks the performance of the equity securities of publicly-traded large-, mid-, and small-capitalization U.S. and non-U.S. companies in developed and emerging markets that are selected based on a list of products and services that enable the practice of distributed energy generation. The fund will invest all, or substantially all, of its assets in the component securities that make up the index. It is non-diversified.
name: SoFi Smart Energy ETF
